commit.title: Add a test build on NixOS to GitLab CI.
commit.message:
Add a test build on NixOS to GitLab CI.

We can't run the test-suite until #5975 is fixed.
We pin default.nix again to make the CI build predictable.
As in Windows builds, we need to override the default before_script.
